               <msContents>
                  <summary>Book of magic including: F<locus target="#3r"/>-21v ፍካሬ ፲ወ፪ ክዋከብት Explanation (Astrological Calculations) for the Twelve Stars.   F<locus target="#21v"/>-30r: Formulae for various calculations: Cryptic Calculations for keeper angel, ሐሳበ ዐቃቤ (<locus target="#21v"/>), for rain (<locus target="#22r"/>), for love (<locus target="#22r"/>), for property (<locus target="#22v"/>), for position (<locus target="#22v"/>), for theft (<locus target="#23r"/>), for sex (<locus target="#23v"/>), for Yodit (<locus target="#23v"/>), for enemies (<locus target="#24r"/>), for man and woman considering marriage (<locus target="#24r"/>), for mountains (<locus target="#24v"/>), the sign for knowing if someone is ill (<locus target="#25r"/>), for pregnancy (<locus target="#25v"/>), for a good marriage for a man and woman  (<locus target="#25v"/>), for bearing a son (<locus target="#26r"/>), for bad fortunes and for good fortune (<locus target="#26v"/>). F<locus target="#30r"/>-33v: Book of fortune telling, መጽሐፈ ኮቦር.  F<locus target="#34r"/>-48r: The Book of the Wisdom of the Magi, መጽሐፈ ሰዓልት ጥበበ ዘረደሽት.  F<locus target="#48r"/>-55r: Further Astrological Calculations in Thirty Sections. F<locus target="#55r"/>-58v: Further Calculations ሐሳበ, for travel (ፍኖት), for mountains (አድባር), for property (ሐብት), for the date of death (ዕለተ ሞት), etc., incomplete at the ending.</summary>
